parameters:
Oh, you must be the rumored magical girl. Your name was
Seraphier, if I recall...

Feel free to conduct your investigation, but please don't
interfere with my research.

Captured children... Ah, you mean the test subjects? They're
in the back room.

The experiments are already complete, so you can take them
with you if you like.
It seems there are no traps in this area.
